05:34.840 --> 05:35.840
Terima kasih, Xu.

05:35.880 --> 05:36.280
Bukan,

05:37.500 --> 05:38.300
terima kasih.

05:38.540 --> 05:39.080
Pak Xu.

05:39.720 --> 05:41.080
