36:06.480 --> 36:07.280
beri tahu aku.

36:07.860 --> 36:08.280
Baik.

36:09.980 --> 36:10.580
Lagi pula,

36:11.480 --> 36:12.020
Zheng.

36:13.300 --> 36:14.840
Lain kali kalau bicara hati-hati sedikit,

36:14.840 --> 36:16.040
